{"type":"message","id":"af8a78fd","parentId":"e15aeafd","timestamp":"2026-07-04T19:24:23.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02d46900285e4a47af837201","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-publish/li-post.sh \"264468965\" text \"𝗠𝗢𝘀𝘁 𝗳𝗼𝘂𝗻𝗱𝗲𝗿𝘀 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗼𝘃𝗲𝗿𝗺𝗲𝗱𝗶𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘁𝗵𝗲𝗶𝗿 𝗽𝗿𝗼𝗱𝘂𝗰𝘁 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝘂𝗻𝗱𝗲𝗿𝗺𝗲𝗱𝗶𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗱𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗿𝗶𝗯𝘂𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻.\n\nYou've got the best product in your category. Congratulations.\n\nNo one knows.\n\nMeanwhile, your competitor with the \\\"good enough\\\" product is on every podcast, every newsletter, every LinkedIn feed. They're winning because they showed up.\n\nHere's the uncomfortable truth:\n\nBuilding something great is the baseline. If you're not distributing, you're not building a business — you're building a hobby.\n\nThe founders who win aren't the ones with the perfect product. They're the ones who ship, talk about it, ship again, and keep talking.\n\nWhat's one distribution channel you've been avoiding because it feels \\\"not ready yet\\\"?\n\n#Startups #Entrepreneurship #Distribution #Growth #FounderLife\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-publish/li-post.sh \\\"264468965\\\" text \\\"𝗠𝗢𝘀𝘁 𝗳𝗼𝘂𝗻𝗱𝗲𝗿𝘀 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗼𝘃𝗲𝗿𝗺𝗲𝗱𝗶𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘁𝗵𝗲𝗶𝗿 𝗽𝗿𝗼𝗱𝘂𝗰𝘁 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝘂𝗻𝗱𝗲𝗿𝗺𝗲𝗱𝗶𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗱𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗿𝗶𝗯𝘂𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻.\\n\\nYou've got the best product in your category. Congratulations.\\n\\nNo one knows.\\n\\nMeanwhile, your competitor with the \\\\\\\"good enough\\\\\\\" product is on every podcast, every newsletter, every LinkedIn feed. They're winning because they showed up.\\n\\nHere's the uncomfortable truth:\\n\\nBuilding something great is the baseline. If you're not distributing, you're not building a business — you're building a hobby.\\n\\nThe founders who win aren't the ones with the perfect product. They're the ones who ship, talk about it, ship again, and keep talking.\\n\\nWhat's one distribution channel you've been avoiding because it feels \\\\\\\"not ready yet\\\\\\\"?\\n\\n#Startups #Entrepreneurship #Distribution #Growth #FounderLife\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783193058145,"responseId":"411Jao_8JY3J1PIPjvXaOA"}}
