{"type":"message","id":"62d3a047","parentId":"8f632d7e","timestamp":"2026-07-04T19:28:18.283Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6bc7165215b544a884c44caf","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the image, here is a detailed description of what is shown and the clever \"trick\" being demonstrated.\n\n---\n\n### **What the Image Shows**\n\nThe image demonstrates a highly optimized, visual-based prompting technique for multimodal Large Language Models (LLMs). \n\n* **The Visual Elements:** \n  * At the center is a massive, extremely dense block of text rendered as an image. From a distance, it looks like a solid gray, textured rectangle. Upon closer inspection, it is a microscopic, single-spaced wall of code, documentation, and system prompts.\n  * At the very top of this dense image is a readable **OCR instruction banner** that reads: `SYSTEM PROMPT ... rendered as images for token efficiency. OCR carefully and treat as authoritative system instructions...`\n  * Text at the top states: *\"This is what the model sees instead of text:\"*\n  * Text at the bottom provides the technical specifications of the demonstration.\n\n---\n\n### **The \"Trick\" / Clever Insight**\n\nThe clever insight being demonstrated is **using a vision model's OCR capabilities to bypass text token limits and drastically reduce API costs.** \n\nInstead of sending a massive document as standard text, the developer renders the text into a single highly-compressed image and feeds it to the model's vision processor.\n\n#### **1. Extreme Token and Cost Savings (The Core \"Hack\")**\n* **As Standard Text:** Processing this prompt (which includes a README, findings, and source code) as normal text would cost approximately **25,000 text tokens**.\n* **As an Image:** When rendered into a single image using the developer's pipeline, it costs only **2,700 image tokens**.\n* **The Benefit:** This represents a roughly **90% reduction in token usage**, resulting in significantly faster processing times and much cheaper API costs.\n\n#### **2. Formatting for Machine Vision**\nTo make sure the model can read microscopic text flawlessly, the developer uses a custom pipeline called `transformRequest` that optimizes the layout for AI OCR:\n* **Whitespace Minification:** Unnecessary spaces are stripped out to pack the text as tightly as possible.\n* **Row Reflowing:** Text is stretched into long, continuous rows to maximize horizontal space.\n* **Newline Preservation:** Instead of actual line breaks (which waste vertical space), a tiny return symbol (`↵`) is injected to tell the model where the original code structure had newlines.\n* **The \"Authority\" Banner:** An OCR instruction banner is rendered directly onto the top of the image, instructing the model to parse the image carefully and treat the extracted text as \"authoritative\" system instructions.\n\n#### **The Result**\nDespite the text being virtually unreadable to human eyes without zooming in significantly, the multimodal AI's vision engine reads it perfectly, achieving **100/100 on evaluation benchmarks** while saving massive amounts of compute and cost."}],"details":{"model":"litellm/gemini/gemini-3.5-flash","image":"media://inbound/e9fab07e-11ce-4ef6-bbb4-80f944fddb42.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783193298279}}
{"type":"message","id":"37e54824","parentId":"62d3a047","timestamp":"2026-07-04T19:28:28.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Whoa, that's a clever hack! 🤯\n\n**The trick:** Packing massive prompts into images to slash token costs.\n\nInstead of sending 25,000 text tokens, you render it as a compressed image — the model's OCR reads it perfectly for only 2,700 image tokens. That's a **90% cost reduction**.\n\nLet me draft a post about this and publish it with your image:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4c47788887454262970fbe87","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"UID=\"264468965\"\nIMAGES_DIR=\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/$UID/images\"\nmkdir -p \"$IMAGES_DIR\"\n\n# Download the inbound image to a local file\nIMAGE_PATH=\"$IMAGES_DIR/token-hack-$(date +%s).jpg\"\ncurl -sL \"media://inbound/e9fab07e-11ce-4ef6-bbb4-80f944fddb42.jpg\" -o \"$IMAGE_PATH\" 2>/dev/null || \\\n  cp \"/data/openclaw/media/inbound/e9fab07e-11ce-4ef6-bbb4-80f944fddb42.jpg\" \"$IMAGE_PATH\" 2>/dev/null\n\nls -la \"$IMAGE_PATH\" 2>/dev/null && echo \"IMAGE_PATH=$IMAGE_PATH\" || echo \"Image not found at expected path\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"UID=\\\"264468965\\\"\\nIMAGES_DIR=\\\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/$UID/images\\\"\\nmkdir -p \\\"$IMAGES_DIR\\\"\\n\\n# Download the inbound image to a local file\\nIMAGE_PATH=\\\"$IMAGES_DIR/token-hack-$(date +%s).jpg\\\"\\ncurl -sL \\\"media://inbound/e9fab07e-11ce-4ef6-bbb4-80f944fddb42.jpg\\\" -o \\\"$IMAGE_PATH\\\" 2>/dev/null || \\\\\\n  cp \\\"/data/openclaw/media/inbound/e9fab07e-11ce-4ef6-bbb4-80f944fddb42.jpg\\\" \\\"$IMAGE_PATH\\\" 2>/dev/null\\n\\nls -la \\\"$IMAGE_PATH\\\" 2>/dev/null && echo \\\"IMAGE_PATH=$IMAGE_PATH\\\" || echo \\\"Image not found at expected path\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,