{"type":"message","id":"89d40695-0722-435a-aa8a-444ff58dcbd3","parentId":"48f3e008-7c7a-49bc-b601-7f41efef4c86","timestamp":"2026-07-05T06:14:53.950Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📝 Post 3/3 — Personal development & mindset\n\n𝗖𝗼𝗻𝘀𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗲𝗻𝗰𝘆 𝗯𝗲𝗮𝘁𝘀 𝗶𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗻𝘀𝗶𝘁𝘆 𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗿𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗺𝗲.\n\nBut we keep betting on intensity.\n\nThe 14-hour sprint. The weekend warrior. The January 1st resolution. All gas, no steering. And then we burn out, disappear for months, and start over.\n\nThe people who win aren't the ones who go hardest. They're the ones who keep going.\n\n- Two posts a week, every week, beats ten posts one week and zero the next\n- 30 minutes of focus daily beats three hours on Sunday\n- One meaningful conversation a day beats ten networking events a year\n\nThe math is brutal: show up 1% better every day and you're 37x better in a year. Skip three months and you're at zero.\n\nYour brand, your skills, your network — they compound. But only if you keep adding to them.\n\nWhat's one thing you can commit to doing every day this month?\n\n#Mindset #Consistency #Growth #PersonalDevelopment #Habits\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━\nSource: evergreen"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783232093936,"idempotencyKey":"9cb8fc54-e22c-4727-9bac-95c63749982d:message-tool:DKQkutOThczUE6RRsUqZhdhi:call_00b5ad0bd520429baef9cbab"},"appendMode":"side"}
